```

---

**`.cursorrules`** — Cursor AI rules file, place at repo root
```
You are working on mms-accounts — MidManStudio's authentication and account management
portal. Stack: Leptos 0.8 (Rust → WebAssembly, CSR), Supabase, Cloudflare Pages.

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
ABSOLUTE RULES — NEVER VIOLATE UNDER ANY CIRCUMSTANCES
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

1. NO EMOJIS — EVER. Not in code, templates, strings, comments, UI text, or anywhere
   else. All icons must be inline SVG elements defined as Leptos components.

2. COMPONENT-DRIVEN ONLY. Every distinct UI element is a named #[component] fn.
   No monolithic render functions. Split early, split often.

3. NO JAVASCRIPT FILES. All behaviour lives in Rust. No .js files, no script tags.

4. SVG ICONS ONLY. All icons are components in src/components/icons/mod.rs.
   Each icon is a #[component] fn returning an <svg> element with currentColor stroke.

5. HASH ROUTING ONLY (CSR). Routes are read from window.location.hash. No leptos_router
   url-based routing. The app.rs router matches on hash string.

6. ASYNC = spawn_local ONLY. Use wasm_bindgen_futures::spawn_local for all async work.
   No tokio, no std::thread, no block_on.

7. HTTP = reqwest ONLY. All Supabase API calls via reqwest. No JS fetch wrappers.

8. STORAGE = gloo-storage ONLY. JWT and session data via gloo_storage::LocalStorage.

9. CSS CUSTOM PROPERTIES ONLY. No hardcoded color/spacing values in CSS. Use :root
   variables. No inline styles except for dynamic runtime values (e.g. widths from state).

10. LEPTOS 0.8 PATTERNS:
    - Signals:  let (val, set_val) = signal(initial_value);
    - Effects:  Effect::new(move |_| { ... });
    - Children: .into_any() for conditional view branches
    - Input:    event_target_value(&ev) to read input events
    - Props:    #[prop(default = ...)] for optional props

═══════════════════════════════════════════
DESIGN SYSTEM — ALWAYS USE THESE TOKENS
═══════════════════════════════════════════

Colors (CSS vars defined in styles/main.css):
  --cobalt:       #0047ab   (primary)
  --cobalt-light: #4169e1   (primary hover / gradient end)
  --cyan-neon:    #00d4ff   (accent / glow)
  --crimson:      #dc143c   (destructive / alert)
  --bg-base:      #040812   (page background)
  --bg-surface:   #070f1f   (card / panel background)
  --text-primary: #e8edf8
  --text-secondary:#8fa0c0
  --text-muted:   #4a5880
  --border-subtle:rgba(65,105,225,0.18)

Typography:
  --font-display: 'Orbitron', monospace      (headings, labels, buttons)
  --font-body:    'Rajdhani', sans-serif      (body text, forms)
  --font-mono:    'JetBrains Mono', monospace (code, metadata, badges)

═══════════════════════════════════
PROJECT STRUCTURE
═══════════════════════════════════

src/
  lib.rs                     — WASM entry point, mounts App
  app.rs                     — App component, hash router, auth context
  supabase/
    mod.rs
    client.rs                — SupabaseClient struct, constants
    auth.rs                  — sign_up, sign_in, sign_out, get_user, update_profile
  components/
    mod.rs
    icons/
      mod.rs                 — ALL SVG icon components
    ui/
      mod.rs                 — Button, Input, Card, Badge, Spinner
    auth/
      mod.rs                 — AuthPage wrapper
      login.rs               — LoginForm
      signup.rs              — SignupForm
      oauth_buttons.rs       — GitHub / Google OAuth buttons
    landing/
      mod.rs                 — LandingPage
      hero.rs                — HeroSection
      features.rs            — FeaturesSection
    dashboard/
      mod.rs                 — DashboardPage, shell
      sidebar.rs             — DashboardSidebar
      header.rs              — DashboardHeader
      overview.rs            — OverviewView
      profile.rs             — ProfileView
    admin/
      mod.rs                 — AdminPage, shell
      stats.rs               — AdminStats cards
      user_table.rs          — UserTable
styles/
  main.css                   — All styles

═══════════════════════════════════
SUPABASE API PATTERNS
═══════════════════════════════════

Base URL: SUPABASE_URL constant in client.rs
Auth endpoints:
  POST /auth/v1/signup                  — register
  POST /auth/v1/token?grant_type=password — login
  GET  /auth/v1/user                    — get current user (Bearer token)
  POST /auth/v1/logout                  — sign out
  POST /auth/v1/user  (PATCH method)    — update user metadata
REST endpoints:
  GET  /rest/v1/profiles?id=eq.{uid}   — get profile
  PATCH /rest/v1/profiles?id=eq.{uid}  — update profile
Headers always needed: apikey: ANON_KEY, Content-Type: application/json
Auth headers: Authorization: Bearer {access_token}
